name: Ninomae Ina'nis (Hololive) all outfits
description:
🐙 It's tako time! This updated version features 4 outfits as well as a generic ninomae ina'nis tag for all your other needs. Check the tags for examples.

Works at weight 1. Made with my Lora guide.

Has trouble with mismatched sleeves/thighhighs, sadly. Also the 4th outfit had very few images so don't judge it harshly.

I put a lot of effort into my Loras, if you like my work consider leaving me a tip :)
